title: Cocoaccino's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Kosher, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Dairy kosher cafe and restaurant offering vegetarian food and fish, coffee and bagels. Menu has veggie burgers, sushi (with veggie and brown rice option), veggie wrap, falafel wrap, soups, hummus platter, burritos, salads (could build your own). The smoothies can be requested vegan, has plant-based milk for coffee and tea. Staff is aware about food allergies, and no shellfish is used. The owners also own Accents Grill restaurant (non-veg) that's in the same plaza. Closed Saturday.
